more about light

“Just as one candle lights another and can light thousands of other candles,
so one heart illuminates another heart and can illuminate thousands of other hearts.” What is this?
“Only when we are brave enough to explore the darkness will we discover the infinite power of our light.”
“Light must come from inside.

“Then God said, 'Let there be light'; and there was light.” The Good News: Light is hope,
wisdom and goodness — God brings us that and it'll never go away. “Jesus answered,
'Are there not twelve hours in the day? If anyone walks in the day, he does not stumble,
because he sees the light of this world.